    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is the one you've been waiting for! We are thrilled to offer this absolute gem that is in truly mint condition. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor, with a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that has been meticulously cared for. If you're looking for perfection and a vehicle that needs absolutely nothing but a new driver, this stunning beauty is ready for you!",
